manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Every Night Starts with A Dream There’s something special about bedtime. The stories we tell, the softness of a warm bed, and the little stuffed friends that we can’t live without. At Dream Factory, we’re inspired by the magic of bedtime. We tell our stories through cozy bedding, playful bathroom accessories and whimsical window curtains. Have a good night every night and come dream with us.

Dreams Come True Designed by moms Approved by kids. As mothers, we want the best for our young dreamers. Each design is carefully crafted to be soft, comfortable, durable, and easy to care for. This goes hand in hand for each whimsical pattern we design. We listen to the playful stories our kids tell. We echo their colorful imagination in our bedding, bath accessories, and window curtains. The Quality of your dreams Carefully crafted designs call for consciously sourced production. At Dream Factory, quality production is our priority. We select from the best factories to produce our styles safely and with proper care. We use fabrics that feel good on your children’s skin so they are comfortable all night long. We make your life (and ours) a little bit easier with durable fabrics that maintain its softness and vibrant colors wash after wash. Easy to care for We know from experience that your little one’s bedding has to be durable. They sleep all night in it and jump on it during the day. At Dream Factory, we designed each bed to withstand wear and tear with durable fabrics. Our styles are machine washable so they can be cared for easily. The colors will stay vibrant and touch will always be soft. Each style can be played in, lived in and dreamed in. What's included? Bring your little one’s imagination to life with Dream Factory. Making the bed of their dreams is simple with our curated bed in a bag. Our Bed in a bag includes a comforter, flat sheet, fitted sheet, pillowcase and a sham. It’s the perfect way to enliven their room with fun patterns that they will love and comfort that you can trust.
